    </list></note><note id="eip-568" class="os-teacher"><label>Teacher Edition</label><para id="eip-idm2236496">The Learning Objectives in this section will help your students master the following TEKS:</para> 
<list id="fs-id1171659477888">
  <item>(4) Science concepts. The student knows and applies the laws governing motion in a variety of situations. The student is expected to: 

